Author: datoasia
Title: ✅[ANN] [ICO] ✅DATO ✅ First targeted advertisement database on blockchain
Body: First targeted advertisement database on blockchain  url https://www.dato.asia/ github https://github.com/datoasia facebook https://www.facebook.com/DATO-1650249821688532 twitter https://twitter.com/DATO53474167 telegram https://t.me/joinchat/HBKcfVE3Ry5Y6dzKdgZY3A   We are from Tokyo, Japan.  dato.asia is presenting you a blockchain database for targeted audience. We are creating blockchain database with potential customers preferences using social platforms such as facebook, VK, twitter, etc. Users are not identified so there is no data protection issue. Any advertisement campaign will be able to use our smart contract, pay a fee in DATO and extract any information they need from any customer base. If the advertiser needs, we can create custom requests and expand our database for that particular point of entry. There is no limit on database options, custom requests or any other options. Very expandable and limitless. Custom requests made for free, as it good for expansion. We start ICO on 31-01-2018 just for 7 days. 1 DATO = 0.002 ETH, hardcap 22 000 ETH.  Thank you, post any questions you like!  DATO team
